<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="30Mar1929"><font color="red">30 March 1929</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): Contract not signed yet. I am trying to revise my text but am stupified still more by iodine. Try to get a copy of the pamphlet issued by Grosvenor House Hotel, Park Lane. The illustration about me will amuse you. </div>
